bandmc: Fast Monte Carlo for BAND

Uses deuterium tagged DIS generator from Wim Cosyn

## Compiling 

In directory with "bandmc" repository:

$ mkdir build
$ ls
bandmc  build
$ cd build
$ cmake ../bandmc
$ make

## Running

$ ./bandmc [N events] [N background] [radiation on/off {1,0}] [smearing on/off {1,0}]

## Required data files

1. Data tables for generator (included in repository).

2. Inclusive electron skim ROOT file
